title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 74: Featuring Paul Bissonnette
description:
Old pal Biz Nasty joins the show for Episode 74. The fellas open up with some words about the Humboldt Broncos tragedy in Canada. Next, they discuss each of the eight playoffs series and offer predictions. Then the boys drop some major news about the future of Spittin' Chiclets. Be sure to tune in.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
